snippet.textDisplay: Hi Steve. Not sure if you’ll ever read my post, but as a person who is clinically depressed and has spontaneous anxiety attacks, I can relate to those deep dark holes that on some days feels impossible to get out of. As your fans, know we love and support you, and appreciate your bravery to explain what’s going on. But never ever apologize to us for what you go through, because remember, mental health is a real thing, and whether people understand or not, it’s not your fault. You be you. We’ll be here for you, always watching your amazing creations. And if it takes longer, take your time!! Don’t listen to negative people (it def doesn’t help). We will rewatch episodes 🥰🥰 Much love to you.

Been worried a bit...
Are you ok?
